import React from 'react'
import { GridItem, Flex, Text } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const Nav = () => {
  return (
    <GridItem colStart={2} colSpan={1} p={3}>
      <Flex>
        <Link to='/'>
          <Text fontSize='md' mr={8}>
            Home{' '}
          </Text>
        </Link>
      </Flex>
    </GridItem>
  )
}

export default Nav
